            </span>
            <div id="arrow-tooltip" style="display:none; position: absolute; bottom: 55px; right: 20px; background: #fff; color: #333; border-radius: 6px; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.15); padding: 8px 16px; font-size: 0.95rem; z-index: 30;">
